'''Megalodon''' is an {{Rarity|Exotic}} fish found in the [[Ancient Isle]].

== Description ==
{{Description|The Megalodon is a gigantic predatory shark known for its enormous size. It possesses a large mouth with many serrated teeth which can easily rip through anything in its way. They went extinct around 3.6 million years ago, during the early Pliocene epoch. They are one of the apex predators of the Ancient Isle, and will put up an incredible fight when hooked.|Bestiary Entry}}

